author: George Lee
title: Number of virus patients in ICUs stabilise - NPHET data
description: There are some positive signs about the spread of the coronavirus in the most recent data from the National Public Health Emergency Team. One is that the number of Covid-19 patients in ICUs appears to have stabilised.
content:
There are some positive signs about the spread of the coronavirus in the most recent data from the National Public Health Emergency Team.
One is that the number of Covid-19 patients in Intensive Care Units appears to have stabilised.
